text: Rajeev Ram and Bobby Reynolds were the defending champions, but Ram chose not to compete in doubles. Reynolds chose to play with Robert Kendrick, but they lost against Treat Conrad Huey and Harsh Mankad in the first round. Stephen Huss and Joseph Sirianni won in the final 1–6, 6–2, [13–11] against Chris Guccione and Frank Moser. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Doubles Draw * Doubles Qualifying Draw Baton Rouge Pro Tennis Classic - Doubles
